Class WebServiceContextAdapter

java.lang.Object
  com.i2group.apollo.rest.WebServiceContextAdapter
All Implemented Interfaces:
WebServiceContext
public final class WebServiceContextAdapter
extends Object
implements WebServiceContext

An implementation of WebServiceContext that includes the facility to be created from the separate ServletContext and HttpServletRequest that REST resources have.

Since:
4.1
